China Investment in Latin America Rises Threefold, Deloitte Says

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-06-22T12:28:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/china-investment-in-latin-america-rises-threefold-deloitte-says.html
Chinese investment in  Brazil ,
Argentina and  Chile  rose almost threefold in the 12 months
through May, according to  Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu Ltd .  Investment surged to $15.6 billion from $4.04 billion in
the same period a year earlier, Deloitte said in a report,
citing data from Mergermarket.  Of the total for the latest 12-month period, 59 percent was
in Brazil and almost 41 percent in Argentina, Deloitte said. The
remainder was invested in Chile, according to the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas in Madrid at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  